title: Bobby’s Girlfriend Does Something Gross + Bobby’s Mailbag: Listener Wants To Return Adopted Puppy + Granger Smith's Ongoing Legal Battles
itunes:title: Bobby’s Girlfriend Does Something Gross + Bobby’s Mailbag: Listener Wants To Return Adopted Puppy + Granger Smith's Ongoing Legal Battles
description:
Bobby’s girlfriend Caitlin joins the show with an update on their quarantine life. They share things they’ve learned about each other and Caitlin reveals something gross she does to Bobby. We open up the mailbag from a listener who adopted a puppy for quarantine, but now wants to return it. Plus, we talk with Granger Smith about his new song and constant legal battles he faces with his “Yee Yee” trademark.
